videos.description: Arkansas State's B.J. Edmonds deflects a pass with one hand and hauls it in early in the game.
videos.headline: Arkansas State forces turnover on incredible one-handed INT

videos.description: Middle Tennessee's Terelle West breaks through the line and scores on a 45-yard rumble to make it 7-3 .
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee on the board with 45-yard TD run

videos.description: Middle Tennessee scores on a crazy-pick 6 return, but Kyle Wilson is ruled down where he made the interception at the 1-yard line.
videos.headline: Unbelievable Middle Tennessee pick-6 ruled down

videos.description: Middle Tennessee's Darius Harris breaks through the line and forces a fumble that D.J. Sanders returns for the 54-yard score to go up 14-3.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee blows game open with strip-sack and score

videos.description: Justice Hansen caps the 13-play drive by keeping the read-option and powering through the goal line to make it 14-10.
videos.headline: Hansen powers in Arkansas State score

videos.description: Brent Stockstill drops back and throws a beautiful ball to Ruben Garnett, who beats his defender before half for the score.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee extends lead before half with 31-yard TD strike

videos.description: Middle Tennessee head coach Rick Stockstill says his team needs to build momentum after scoring late in the first half.
videos.headline: Stockstill wants more consistent second half

videos.description: Tavares Thomas takes the handoff and rumbles into the end zone to go up 28-10.
videos.headline: Thomas lowers shoulder for Middle Tennessee TD

videos.description: Justin McInnis catches the screen pass and rips it 20 yards to the end zone as Arkansas State trails 28-17.
videos.headline: Score off screen pass keeps Arkansas State in it

videos.description: The referee collides with the Middle Tennessee receiver and Brent Stockstill's pass nails the ref.
videos.headline: Referee gets drilled by pass

videos.description: Brent Stockstill rolls left and throws all the way across his body as B.J. Edmonds comes up with the interception.
videos.headline: Edmonds makes second bobbling INT for Arkansas State

videos.description: Arkansas State is driving into the red zone, but O.J. Johnson comes down with the interception off the big collision.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee prevents score with tip-drill INT

videos.description: Arkansas State punter Cody Grace throws a beautiful fade ball on a fake punt and Chris Murray comes down with the catch.
videos.headline: Arkansas State keeps drive alive with fake punt

videos.description: Brent Stockstill delivers a 30-yard strike to Shane Tucker who splits the safeties and scores to make it 35-23.
videos.headline: Tucker splits defense to extend Middle Tennessee's lead

videos.description: Arkansas State is within five after Christian Booker burns his defender and comes down with the 41-yard score.
videos.headline: Hansen connects with Booker on 41-yard TD

videos.description: Coach Rick Stockstill is proud of his whole team after his son led Middle Tennessee to a 35-30 victory over Arkansas State.
videos.headline: Middle Tennessee wins after coach spends $10,000 on student tickets
